<Layout title="Recon-Pipeline">

<h1>Recon-Pipeline</h1>

<h2>Bug-bounty reconnaissance pipeline</h2>

<p>
 An automated reconnaissance workflow using tools such as Subfinder, HTTPX,
    Naabu, Nuclei and FFUF. Designed to assist with legal bug bounty and attack
    surface discovery activities.
</p>

<hr>

<h2>Current Status</h2>

<p>
Active Development
</p>

<hr>

<h2>Technology Stack</h2>

<ul>
    <li>n8n</li>
    <li>Docker</li>
    <li>Subfinder</li>
    <li>HTTPX</li>
    <li>Naabu</li>
    <li>Ffuf</li>
    <li>Nuclei</li>
</ul>

<hr>

<h2>Project Goals</h2>

<ul>
    <li>Determine sub-domains from hackerone data</li>
    <li>Identify live hosts and web services</li>
    <li>Perform automated port discovery</li>
    <li>Detect known vulnerabilities using Nuclei</li>
    <li>Automate content discovery with FFUF</li>
    <li>Reduce manual reconnaissance effort</li>
</ul>

